{
  "texts": [
    "Given that ChatGPT's training was based on internet data up until September 2021, its pro ciency mirrors the knowledge and biases in that dataset.",
    "Nevertheless, the evolution of LLMs is swift, as Johnson et al. (2023) showed with a signi cant accuracy improvement in cancer information within just two weeks [41].",
    "This underscores the need for ongoing evaluation of LLMs across various medical elds.Our study's robust methodology, including anonymizing LLM-speci c answer features, randomizing responses, and introducing intervals between rating sessions, enhanced the credibility of our conclusions.",
    "Nonetheless, there are limitations, such as the rater's subjectivity, which we attempted to mitigate by employing an experienced pediatrician and a multi-round rating approach.",
    "The limited number of questions per disease category also necessitates caution in generalizing LLM-Chatbots' performance."
  ]
}